Avatar The Last Airbender TV series

Video: MPEG4 Video (H264) 960x720 29.97fps
Audio: Dolby AC3 48000Hz stereo
Subtitle: None
File size: 250-350MB

First, yes, this is the upscale version of the DVD Avatar. However, I believe that this one has the best quality you could find on the internet with almost no ghosting in the first 4 episodes (It's still there but you wont even notice), thinner lines, sharper and cleaner images. The torrent contains:


. Full 3 seasons of the series (61 eps)
. 3 chibi shorts
. The animated graphic novel: Escape from the spirit world
. The un-aired pilot episode without commentary
. The unofficial OST


